\begin_layout Section
Propogating Changes
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The calculation task is seperated among the objects, in such that the bag
 triggers calculated values in the intravenous and vise versa.
 This is in contrast to one centerlized calculation procedure.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Centerlized Calculation
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Whenever a user sets a new value to any of the fields, a calculation procedure
 is executed.
 The procedure consists of branches according to the user-cases, in each
 branch there are three values being used to calculate the other values.
\end_layout

